    ## Use when

    Presenting a <eds-link eds-href="/components/form/form.html">Form</eds-link> entry or <eds-link eds-href="/patterns/display-data.html">display data</eds-link> that combines:
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/label/label.html">Label</eds-link> (required)
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/microcopy/microcopy.html">Microcopy</eds-link>
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/inline-alert/inline-alert.html">Inline Alert</eds-link>
    
    with one of the following:
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/input/input.html">Input</eds-link>
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/select/select.html">Select</eds-link>
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/textarea/textarea.html">Textarea</eds-link>
    - A single <eds-link eds-href="/components/checkbox/checkbox.html">Checkbox</eds-link> with error validation
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/checkbox-group/checkbox-group.html">Checkbox Group</eds-link>
    - <eds-link eds-href="/components/radio-group/radio-group.html">Radio Group</eds-link>
    - <eds-link eds-href="/patterns/display-data.html">Display data</eds-link> text

    ### Don't use when
    Presenting a single <eds-link eds-href="/components/checkbox/checkbox.html">Checkbox</eds-link> with *no* error validation.

    ## Visual style

    ### Anatomy and construction
    - Always include a Label as the first part of a <eds-link eds-href="/components/field-group/field-group.html">Field Group</eds-link>. 
    - Optionally use <eds-link eds-href="/components/microcopy/microcopy.html">Microcopy</eds-link> to provide additional context either above or below the data entry controls or data display text.
    - Always wrap multiple <eds-link eds-href="/components/checkbox/checkbox.html">Checkboxes</eds-link> in a <eds-link eds-href="/components/checkbox-group/checkbox-group.html">Checkbox Group</eds-link> within a <eds-link eds-href="/components/field-group/field-group.html">Field Group</eds-link>. 
    - Always wrap multiple <eds-link eds-href="/components/radio-button/radio-button.html">Radio Buttons</eds-link> in a <eds-link eds-href="/components/radio-group/radio-group.html">Radio Group</eds-link> within a <eds-link eds-href="/components/field-group/field-group.html">Field Group</eds-link>. 
    - Always make an <eds-link eds-href="/components/inline-alert/inline-alert.html">Inline Alert</eds-link> the last component in the group if present. 
    {% endfilter %}
    
